scenes.description: Underwater animation of Gawr Gura with background music.
Gawr Gura's birthday stream MC section. She greets the chat and talks about being nervous.

subtitles.original: Hi.
subtitles.english: Hi.

subtitles.original: Aha! Aha, I thought...
subtitles.english: Aha! Aha, I thought...

subtitles.original: ...I thought I was going to burp,
subtitles.english: ...I thought I was going to burp,

subtitles.original: and then I thought,
subtitles.english: and then I thought,

subtitles.original: imagine if the first thing I say when I'm here...
subtitles.english: imagine if the first thing I say when I'm here...

subtitles.original: ...is just a burp.
subtitles.english: ...is just a burp.

subtitles.original: That would have been quite...
subtitles.english: That would have been quite...

subtitles.original: ...that would have been something.
subtitles.english: ...that would have been something.

subtitles.original: Anyway, hi! Hi!
subtitles.english: Anyway, hi! Hi!

subtitles.original: Hi!
subtitles.english: Hi!

subtitles.original: Hi.
subtitles.english: Hi.

subtitles.original: I was... can you hear me over this...
subtitles.english: I was... can you hear me over this...

subtitles.original: ...jazz band? Let me calm down...
subtitles.english: ...jazz band? Let me calm down...

subtitles.original: ...let me calm down the brass real quick.
subtitles.english: ...let me calm down the brass real quick.

subtitles.original: Oh, is it fine? You hear me.
subtitles.english: Oh, is it fine? You hear me.

subtitles.original: Ah! Hello!
subtitles.english: Ah! Hello!

subtitles.original: It's my birthday today!
subtitles.english: It's my birthday today!

subtitles.original: What was I going to say?
subtitles.english: What was I going to say?

subtitles.original: Oh, I was going to say,
subtitles.english: Oh, I was going to say,

subtitles.original: I was so nervous before the start of the stream.
subtitles.english: I was so nervous before the start of the stream.

subtitles.original: I was just saying "Ah" into my microphone like that,
subtitles.english: I was just saying "Ah" into my microphone like that,

subtitles.original: but like really quietly and like sensually.
subtitles.english: but like really quietly and like sensually.

subtitles.original: Well, not sensually, I was just saying it quietly.
subtitles.english: Well, not sensually, I was just saying it quietly.

subtitles.original: And I was listening to my heartbeat so loud and so hard.
subtitles.english: And I was listening to my heartbeat so loud and so hard.

subtitles.original: You can hear it. I can like hear it in my throat.
subtitles.english: You can hear it. I can like hear it in my throat.

subtitles.original: That's kind of gross, isn't it?
subtitles.english: That's kind of gross, isn't it?

subtitles.original: Ew, did you know there's a skeleton inside you right now?
subtitles.english: Ew, did you know there's a skeleton inside you right now?

subtitles.original: And next to the skeleton, there's like hearts and stuff.
subtitles.english: And next to the skeleton, there's like hearts and stuff.

subtitles.original: Did you know there's like squishy pieces inside of you?
subtitles.english: Did you know there's like squishy pieces inside of you?

subtitles.original: There's a skeleton living inside you,
subtitles.english: There's a skeleton living inside you,

subtitles.original: and he has a collection of other squishy things. Ew.
subtitles.english: and he has a collection of other squishy things. Ew.

subtitles.original: I'm also incredibly fidgety today because I'm so nervous.
subtitles.english: I'm also incredibly fidgety today because I'm so nervous.

subtitles.original: Anyway, today's my birthday.
subtitles.english: Anyway, today's my birthday.
